Class ResolutionIntFilter

  • java.lang.Object
    • javax.swing.text.DocumentFilter
      • gui.saving.ImageSet.ResolutionIntFilter

  • public class ResolutionIntFilter
extends javax.swing.text.DocumentFilter
    The Class ResolutionIntFilter. Filters the input text by checking is it numerical and the values of JTextFiels will not exceed 5000.
